title: Game Developer
longDescription:
You will assist out team in creating games. Accepting developers with minimum 1 year experience and a portfolio.
Languages: English
companyDescription: We are a community committed to reshaping the ro-football scene and leading it into a new era. Your participation, determination and drive will help us push this league forward. Your effort and ideas will play a key role in making this league the best it can be, and together we can set a new standard for the community.
